text: Sky Devils is a 1932 American action comedy movie directed by A. Edward Sutherland and starring Spencer Tracy, George Cooper, Ann Dvorak, Billy Bevan, Yola d'Avril. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * Category:1932 comedy movies Category:1930s action movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies directed by A.
